Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.75,0:02:25.02,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,	{\blur6\fad(100,100)}一心追求奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.02,0:02:30.18,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,	{\blur6\fad(100,100)}在无尽的黑暗中彷徨
