Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.90,0:02:40.77,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,	{\blur6\fad(100,100)}就再也看不到未来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.98,0:02:43.45,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,	{\blur6\fad(100,100)}今宵亦有明月相邀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.61,0:02:46.03,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,	{\blur6\fad(100,100)}虽然还未能吐露真意
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.21,0:02:50.35,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,	{\blur6\fad(100,100)}但心中一直在呐喊着
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.10,0:02:56.34,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,	{\blur6\fad(100,100)}埋藏的感情释放悲鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.52,0:03:01.46,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,	{\blur6\fad(100,100)}坚定的誓言紧握手心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.60,0:03:06.97,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,	{\blur6\fad(100,100)}若能变得更强一点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.16,0:03:10.66,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,	{\blur6\fad(100,100)}眼前的这个天空
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.80,0:03:13.46,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,	{\blur6\fad(100,100)}就能跨越
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.01,0:03:18.64,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,	{\blur6\fad(100,100)}在那前方的未来
